      "title": "The curfew imposed on Colombo ends at eight today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police headquarters said that the police curfew (9) which had been imposed until further notice covering several police divisions in the Western Province will be lifted at 8:00 am.",
        "A police curfew was imposed on the police divisions of Colombo North, Colombo South, Colombo Central, and Nugegoda Division, Galkissa, Kelaniva Division, and Negombo Division belonging to the Western Province from 9.00 pm yesterday until further notice."
      ],
